Privacy Policy
Last updated: August 12, 2022
Easy Voice Recorder & Memos(hereinafter as " Easy Voice Recorder & Memos", "we", "our", or "us") understands the importance of protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information of yours will be collected when you download, install, or use this mobile application (the "App"), and how such information will be used and shared. It also explains choices you have to control the collection, correction and/or deletion of such information. By using our websites and applications, you consent to the policy and to the collection, processing, disclosure and use of your information as described in this policy.
This policy applies only to information we collect in our App and in e-mail, text and other electronic communications sent through or in connection with our App. This policy DOES NOT apply to information that we collect offline, information collected in other apps or websites (including third party websites you may access through the App), or information collected by any third party. These third parties may have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to read before providing information on or through them.
IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS SET FORTH HEREIN, DO NOT USE THE SOFTWARE & SERVICES.
1.What information we collect
A.Information you directly and voluntarily provide to us
If you are a user of Easy Voice Recorder & Memos, we may collect information that you provide to us. The information includes but is not limited to: the content of feedback, and the content of questionnaire answered by you. We use the information to accept users' feedback and will never leak your privacy information.
B. Information automatically collected when you use Easy Voice Recorder & Memos.
We automatically collect information about you when you use our application ("Easy Voice Recorder & Memos"). We will collect information including, but not limited to: your device Internet Protocol ("IP") address, your hardware manufacturer & model, operating system version, screen size, CPU model, unique device identifiers, mobile network information and installed apps, the time and date of your login, the time spent on our applications and other statistics.
C. The photos you submit on Easy Voice Recorder & Memos
We encourage everyone to avoid sending any pictures that may be used to identify themselves in the photos that you upload. Please do not send any photos of yourself that would allow others to identify you. We only want photos of Easy Voice Recorder & Memos. Any use of photos with your likeness is subject to the terms of our Terms of Use. We only use the photos for recognizing and machine learning.
2.How we use collected information
We only use the information you directly and voluntarily provide to us to accept and respond to your feedback.
We may use the information automatically collected when you use Easy Voice Recorder & Memosfor any purpose as below:
A.To personalize our services. We may use your information to understand demographics, customer interest and calculate your consumption of calorie;
B.To help maintain and improve our services. We may use your information to measure the performance of our application and ensure our services are working as intended, such as troubleshooting issues reported from you;
C.To help develop our app and service. We may use your information to modify the applications, services and develop new services.
